The paper deals with deep neural networks operating on raw point cloud data, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The applications mentioned in the abstract, such as robotics and self-driving cars, suggest that the paper could also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper proposes an unsupervised learning method, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
